libperf: Add perf_cpu_map__for_each_cpu() macro

Add the following macro to libperf:

  perf_cpu_map__for_each_cpu()

And its related functions:

  perf_cpu_map__cpu()
  perf_cpu_map__nr()

That will allow hiding how it is implemented.

